com.vernalis.knime.internal.flowcontrol.nodes.timedloops.abstrct.loopstart

Interface TimedLoopStart

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractChunkTimedLoopStartNodeModel, AbstractTimedLoopStartNodeModel, AbstractVariableTimedLoopStartNodeModel

    public interface TimedLoopStart
    Interface with the methods required for a timed loop start node. These public methods are required to be implemented so that the timed loop end nodes can use them.
    Author:
    Stephen Roughley
